nodes.text: Chull was a male Human Doctor of the Galactic Republic during the Galactic War.

Around 3640 BBY, Chull was stationed at the Kri-Ta Outpost in the Pelath-Ri Marches the planet Voss when the Gormak have stolen vital advanced power cores to use in their war machines against the Voss. Chull tasked a Republic citizen to recover the power cores before the Gormak could fashion them into weaponry.
